flowchart TD
    U([User]) -- question + Qwen key --> WEB[Web Arena\nSPA on port 8080]

    WEB -- POST /api/convene\nSSE stream --> APP[chorus/app.py\nFastAPI]

    APP --> ORC[chorus/orchestra.py\nAsync orchestrator]

    ORC --> R1[engine/researcher.py\nStage 1 Researcher]
    R1 -- DDG search --> DDG[(DuckDuckGo)]
    DDG --> R1
    R1 -- Qwen summarise --> QW[Qwen Cloud\nDashScope intl]
    QW --> R1
    R1 -- engrams --> MEM[(Shared memory pool\nCadran PyStore)]

    ORC --> ANA[chorus/analyzer.py\nCast domain agents]
    ANA -- Qwen JSON call --> QW
    QW -- agent list --> ANA

    ANA --> AG1[Agent A\nneurology]
    ANA --> AG2[Agent B\noptics]
    ANA --> AGN[Agent N\nfinance …]

    AG1 & AG2 & AGN -- asyncio.gather\nparallel --> QW
    AG1 & AG2 & AGN -- DDG search --> DDG
    AG1 & AG2 & AGN -- write position --> MEM

    ORC --> COORD[chorus/coordinator.py\nReconcile findings]
    COORD -- read positions --> MEM
    COORD -- Qwen call --> QW

    ORC --> SYN[chorus/synthesis.py\nFinal document]
    SYN -- read all evidence --> MEM
    SYN -- Qwen call --> QW
    SYN -- Markdown + PDF --> APP

    APP -- post-convene chat --> CHAT[chorus/app.py\n/api/chat]
    CHAT -- recall from memory --> MEM
    CHAT -- Qwen call --> QW
    CHAT -- answer --> WEB

